name: Corps of Cadets Lacrosse Team
description: The Corps of Cadets Lacrosse Team is a club lacrosse team that caters to members of the Corps of Cadets. Competing against outside teams and clubs with a practice and game schedule that works around the cadets time table in the Corps. We provide an open atmosphere where cadets from rookies to veterans can come enjoy and compete in the game of lacrosse. We compete for Texas A&M and the Corps of Cadets in order to promote and further the positive recognition of both.
